item.title: FAQ Collaborative thread
item.dc:creator: Nix
item.description:
Hello Aquanauts

I’ve noticed that many of you turn to the forum for help or clarification regarding your deposits and staking. At the same time, I see that there is a lot of traffic on Discord and not everyone finds answers due to the high demand.

I think it’s a good idea to start this collaborative FAQ and avoid spamming the forum with different questions and posts.

If you have a question, refer to this post, comment, and respond if you know the answer or where to find it. I suggest using the following template:

Issue:
Brief description of the issue:
Date:
Pubkey if need:
Screenshot if possible:
Additional information:

Also, I’m copying @macflapd L2 deposits FAQ. → Discord

Cheers!
